reviewText: I love this show.  Steve and Nick Kroll never fail to deliver the funniest animated show on HBO.  I purchased the non-HD format since it is a cartoon and it looked great on a 1080 TV.
Title: The Life & Times of Tim: Season 3

reviewText: i own all 3 seasons of tim.  it is humor that is based on day to day life.  the characters are likable, no crazy gross humor of throwing up or stuff about bathroom stuff.the dialogue is well written.  fun cameos by random comedians and actors/actresses.
Title: The Life & Times of Tim: Season 3

reviewText: The Life & Times of Tim is one of the funniest shows out there. Season 3 is the last one, so it is sad to see the end. This season is just as great as 1 & 2. The Boss is stellar as usual. The whole cast is great and each episode is extremely funny. Very happy with this purchase and of course love the show. If you are a fan of the first two seasons you need to get Season 3. If you've never seen this show you should.
Title: The Life & Times of Tim: Season 3

reviewText: Love this series and it is evident that this season had a larger production budget by the guest voices that appear throughout. What a shame that this is that last season of the series.
